Assalamualaikum, I am Mr Abdulrahman Bin Humaidan from Kingdom of Saudi Arabia. I had a very serious problems with my teeth and gums. I approached many dentists in my country Saudi Arabia. But many of them gave different opinions regarding the treatment. Non of them satisfied my heart. Moreover, as everyone know that the treatment cost here in Saudi is very expensive. I could have spent and got treated here in Saudi itself, but was not satisfied with the treatment. So one of my friend here in Saudi Arabia recommended and told me the good open options and excellent treatment in India. So I started googling for it. I came to know about Eiliyah Dental care through it. I read many excellent reviews aswel. I called Dr Shamaz and told him regarding my problems. He was so obliged and prepared a tentative treatment chart. I came down to Bangalore one fine day. I went to the Clinic (Eiliyah Dental care). I was so much impressed about this clinical setup. He reviewed my mouth completely. He then prepared a final treatment chart which was very convincing to me. He started the treatment the very next day. First day he completed my Root Canal Treatment (RCT), later two days he did few gum treatment. And 4th day he started with denture work. With in 10 days he completely rehabilitated my mouth. This is all at an very affordable cost, the cost which is just 25% of the estimated cost in Saudi Arabia, using state of the art sufesticated instruments and equipment. Alhamdulillāh now I am very much satisfied and appreciate the skills of the doctors in this dental clinic. Know it is almost more than a year, Alhamdulillāh I am free of all ailments. 

I highly recommend this Eiliyah Dental care for all the people who need dental treatment at an affordable cost. May Allah bless the Eiliyah Dental care and the doctors in it.

Dr Shamaz explains in detail about the condition, it's cause and the treatment he gives.

Recently my dad had excessive tooth sensitivity, and later it was found to be a cavity. Root canal was done, which was perfect.

Dr. Shamaz is humble, not at all money minded. He spent good amount of time in treating, and was not at all in a hurry. He is by far the best dentist I have met.
